				<td colspan="2"><span>Just wondering, are you guys bored?
<br />

<br />
Maybe its because I trade ALOT in bazaar and thats how i make my plat.  I'm always staring at the chat box and at the bazaar search box.
<br />

<br />
Other than that i'm chatting with some ppl that i know, or i'll be in a group in lower tier planes or ldon.  It seems that all that i do revolves around that.  And although its kinda fun after that 200th hour of the same thing over and over again... it gets a bit tedious. 
<br />

<br />
You gotta wonder-- whats the point?  what is this UBERness we strive for-- its nothing more than numbers.  And it takes up entirely too much time for something so trivial.  Anyways just a thought- hope you guys can persuade me otherwise, lol i'm just getting into other hobbies atm so EQ seems kinda bland.
<br />

<br />
Lebash Chordweaver
<br />
56Bard of Terris Thule
<br />
look at my phat lutzhttp://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=769188</span></td>
