				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Are you Guys bored of EQ?<a name="33719"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 8 04 8:11 PM</span></td>
