				<td colspan="2"><span>If you're bored with EQ, I suggest trying out a PvP server.  The element of surprise is always present, and no two fights are exactly the same.  You're not sure what to expect at times, and we still have all that other fun stuff you do on blue servers if you tire of the PvP.  Playing an underpowerd PvP class can be great fun if you can take losing, because when you do win it feels great knowing that you came out on top despite very unfair odds.. don't knock it because 1 vs. 1 PvP is broken, when you get the group vs. group or 2-3 vs. 1 overpowered class PvP, you realize that it's worth it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
